reviewText: History is very much of interest to me as try to become more acquainted with pieces of history that I am not familiar.  It seems as time passes, what I have learned in the past has become fuzzy.  I like having references that I can restore sections of history that I should have remembered from my time in school.  Thanks for making this section of history available.
1997 story on the Vikings was disappointing, I should have checked the date.  It should have been valued at 7.00 or less.
